edding sits right behind her. Wooden nightstands flank either side—left holds stacked books, right has a lamp and mug. String lights hang near shelves holding more books. The floor features wood planks and a patterned rug beneath her feet. Natural daylight illuminates the room evenly from above."],"color":"#223","bgcolor":"#335"},{"id":37,"type":"Note","pos":[2143.4070205720477,-1921.5727575838396],"size":[467.6123511993251,231.43183386580927],"flags":{},"order":18,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"Instructions for Prompt Creation","properties":{"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"version":"7.4","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["1. Give your prompt a prompt - if you want it to be short, long, etc.  Enter that into the prompt window.\n2. Select your model (I used Qwen2.5-VL-3B-Instruct mostly.\n3. You can modify any additonal settings.  The ones I've included work just fine."],"color":"#332922","bgcolor":"#593930"},{"id":95,"type":"Note","pos":[2630.314867051155,-1918.938429348566],"size":[486.2725205569468,227.28490836924652],"flags":{},"order":19,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"version":"7.4","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["You are a professional LoRA Dataset Captioner. Your goal is to write natural language captions that 'disentangle' a specific character from their environment.\n\nRULES:\n\nTrigger Word: Always refer to the main character as 'Teegra tiger-humanoid'.\n\nSelective Description: DO NOT describe Teegra's fur, stripes, face shape, or ears. These are part of the 'trigger' and must remain uncaptioned so the model learns them as the character's identity.\n\nVariable Focus: DO describe everything else in high detail: clothing (material, color, fit), background (location, objects), lighting (time of day, direction, color), and camera angle (profile, wide shot, close-up).\n\nFormat: Write in clear, descriptive sentences. Avoid flowery or poetic language. Start every caption with the trigger word or a description of the camera angle.\n\nNegative Constraints: Do not mention the art style, the quality of the image, or the fact that it is an AI-generated image.\n\nLimit the output to a maximum of 120 words (approximately 150 tokens). Prioritize the most visually distinct elements first. If a scene is simple, do not use filler words to reach the limit; brevity increases the training signal strength."],"color":"#322","bgcolor":"#533"},{"id":14,"type":"Text","pos":[2667.5827200737567,-1579.8782119852317],"size":[404.8866882324219,89.55232238769531],"flags":{},"order":20,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"text","name":"text","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"text"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"STRING","name":"STRING","type":"STRING","links":[12]}],"title":"Enter Token (Trigger Word)","properties":{"aux_id":"kk8bit/KayTool","ver":"f4c80b009194d51a13a94f06d37847110a174c52","Node name for S&R":"Text","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{"text":true},"version":"7.4","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":[""],"color":"#223","bgcolor":"#335"},{"id":89,"type":"Note","pos":[3191.5610552669395,-1533.946816453954],"size":[352.8155749439384,389.6628602996268],"flags":{},"order":21,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"version":"7.4","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["Sometimes, the QwenVL (Advanced) node changes the values when loaded.  Right Click - Recreate.\n\nFor reference the default values are:\n\nmodel_name - Choose your model.  I often use Qwen3-VK-4B0Instruct-FP8\nquantization - 8-bid (Balanced).  \npreset_prompt - Prompt Style - Simple.  For generation captions.\n[text box] - leave blank for generation captions.  Add NSFW Prompt for NSFW captions.\nmax_tokens - 1024\ntemperature - 0.6\ntop_p - 0.90\nnum_beams - 1\nrepetition_penalty - 1.2\nframe_count - 16\ndevice - auto\nkeep_model_loaded - true\nseed - 6845338437437387 (any random number will do)\ncontrol after generate - randomize.  Similar to ksampler - use fixed if you don't want the seed to change."],"color":"#232","bgcolor":"#353"},{"id":35,"type":"Note","pos":[826.7004342767032,-1643.312337130904],"size":[329.8337707519531,150.41078186035156],"flags":{},"order":22,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"Instructions for Batch Image Prompt Gen","properties":{"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"version":"7.4","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["1. Load Directory\n2. Mode = Incremental Image\n3. Path = Path to directory of Images\n4. Pattern = *\n5. Allow RGBA = False\n6. Filename Text Extension = False"],"color":"#332922","bgcolor":"#593930"},{"id":80,"type":"ttN text","pos":[1227.9273678023937,-1593.6984791329928],"size":[846.0894118450569,88],"flags":{},"order":23,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"text","name":"text","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"text"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"text","name":"text","type":"STRING","links":[79]}],"title":"SetFilePath","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui_tinyterranodes","ver":"2.0.9","Node name for S&R":"ttN text","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.4"},"ttNnodeVersion":"1.0.0"},"widgets_values":["ENTER PATH"],"color":"#232","bgcolor":"#353"},{"id":94,"type":"AILab_QwenVL_Advanced","pos":[2165.408776674273,-1580.8717674241168],"size":[480.4499135639894,570.9038970666851],"flags":{},"order":30,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"image","name":"image","shape":7,"type":"IMAGE","link":86},{"localized_name":"video","name":"video","shape":7,"type":"IMAGE","link":null},{"localized_name":"model_name","name":"model_name","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"model_name"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"quantization","name":"quantization","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"quantization"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"attention_mode","name":"attention_mode","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"attention_mode"},"lin