 character as 'Teegra tiger-humanoid'.\n\nSelective Description: DO NOT describe Teegra's fur, stripes, face shape, or ears. These are part of the 'trigger' and must remain uncaptioned so the model learns them as the character's identity.\n\nVariable Focus: DO describe everything else in high detail: clothing (material, color, fit), background (location, objects), lighting (time of day, direction, color), and camera angle (profile, wide shot, close-up).\n\nFormat: Write in clear, descriptive sentences. Avoid flowery or poetic language. Start every caption with the trigger word or a description of the camera angle.\n\nNegative Constraints: Do not mention the art style, the quality of the image, or the fact that it is an AI-generated image.\n\nLimit the output to a maximum of 100 words (approximately 128 tokens). Prioritize the most visually distinct elements first. If a scene is simple, do not use filler words to reach the limit; brevity increases the training signal strength.",128,0.6,0.9,1,1.2,16,true,2484952239,"randomize"],"color":"#28403f","bgcolor":"#374539"},{"id":86,"type":"Note","pos":[3191.4696860413374,-1962.9246869475744],"size":[263.2779296875,88],"flags":{},"order":24,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"NSFW Prompt (Training Captions)","properties":{"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"version":"7.4","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["Analyze the provided image carefully and generate a concise, high-quality caption suitable for LoRA training.\n\nFocus on stable, identity-defining features of the character, including:\nfacial structure and expression\nBreasts and vagina\nhair color, style, and length\nskin tone and notable details (freckles, marks, etc.)\nbody type and apparent age range\nclothing and accessories (only if clearly visible)\n\nUse clear, natural language in a single short paragraph.\nAvoid artistic interpretation, mood, storytelling, camera terms, lighting, background details, or speculative traits.\nDo not invent features that are not visible.\n\nWrite the caption as a neutral, factual description optimized for consistent identity learning."],"color":"#332922","bgcolor":"#593930"},{"id":77,"type":"Label (rgthree)","pos":[-1704.7803794441693,-2461.36915692046],"size":[4852.5390625,250],"flags":{"allow_interaction":true},"order":9,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"BOND QWEN3 VL PROMPT GENERATOR","properties":{"fontSize":250,"fontFamily":"Arial","fontColor":"#ffffff","textAlign":"left","backgroundColor":"transparent","padding":0,"borderRadius":0,"angle":0,"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"version":"7.4","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"color":"#fff0","bgcolor":"#fff0"}],"links":[[9,6,0,9,0,"STRING"],[12,14,0,6,0,"STRING"],[22,12,0,6,1,"STRING"],[43,21,0,34,0,"IMAGE"],[46,46,0,43,0,"STRING"],[47,42,0,43,1,"STRING"],[48,43,0,44,0,"STRING"],[62,9,0,68,0,"STRING"],[63,68,0,69,0,"STRING"],[67,69,0,71,0,"STRING"],[69,44,0,72,0,"STRING"],[71,58,0,75,0,"IMAGE"],[72,74,0,75,1,"IMAGE"],[73,75,0,42,0,"STRING"],[74,74,1,75,14,"INT"],[77,21,1,78,0,"STRING"],[79,80,0,81,0,"STRING"],[80,82,0,21,4,"STRING"],[81,83,0,71,1,"STRING"],[83,84,0,71,2,"STRING"],[86,21,0,94,0,"IMAGE"],[87,94,0,12,0,"STRING"]],"groups":[{"id":2,"title":"Step 1 - Set Up Batch Images","bounding":[1204.175630840353,-1674.2555275064713,900.632114757811,1616.8603312332896],"color":"#8A8","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":4,"title":"Step 2 - Build Prompt","bounding":[2143.445040020042,-1671.186115275026,972.663818359375,676.0903930664062],"color":"#88A","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":5,"title":"File Save","bounding":[2148.3881090790364,-961.7779497272222,685.744159611239,664.6549098817977],"color":"#b58b2a","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":10,"title":"Single Prompt Generator","bounding":[-1625.4686279296875,-1992.5565185546875,1961.8830886389392,2864.6734789438033],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":6,"title":"Step 1 - Set Up Batch Images","bounding":[-1599.3655733891617,-1763.295936229